    "en": {
      "title": "India becomes the lender to Sri Lanka, surpassing China",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In the period of 4 months up to 30th April this year, India has surpassed China as the country that has given the largest amount of loans to Sri Lanka.",
        "Thus, during the same period, India has given a loan of 376.9 million US dollars to Sri Lanka and China has extended a credit facility of 67.9 million US dollars.",
        "However, the all-India credit facility provided to Sri Lanka till June this year is about 3.5 billion US dollars."
      ],
